420
00:29:17.120 --> 00:29:20.480
Is Big Mom already inside?

421
00:29:21.610 --> 00:29:26.540
See, I had an invitation from the last tea party.

422
00:29:27.320 --> 00:29:30.580
But sadly, I was unable to be here.

423
00:29:30.580 --> 00:29:34.160
I had to attend my mother's funeral!

424
00:29:34.160 --> 00:29:36.920
I wrote my reasons in a letter,

425
