638
00:30:40.400 --> 00:30:41.770
Why did you shoot him?!

639
00:30:41.770 --> 00:30:44.530
This is what he was going to say:

640
00:30:45.130 --> 00:30:49.880
"...but guess what Big Mom sent me in response!"

641
00:30:50.490 --> 00:30:53.990
"It was my hospitalized father's head."

642
00:30:54.990 --> 00:30:58.580
"I'm here today to get revenge."

643
00:30:58.580 --> 00:31:00.710
"Open the gate."

644
00:31:00.710 --> 00:31:01.790
Bang.

645
00:31:02.540 --> 00:31:04.840
Bang, he shot.

646
00:31:05.750 --> 00:31:09.550
Two of your men would've been shot.

647
00:31:11.140 --> 00:31:17.760
Is it wrong for me to throw a jelly bean
at him before that could happen?

648
00:31:17.760 --> 00:31:20.080
Rook Bege.

649
00:31:21.930 --> 00:31:25.220
Tell Mama that I made the decision.

650
00:31:27.160 --> 00:31:29.650
This is what you're gonna say now:

651
00:31:30.750 --> 00:31:32.270
"I see."

652
00:31:32.270 --> 00:31:34.740
"Alright then."

653
00:31:36.820 --> 00:31:40.570
He'll be the biggest pain in the ass at the party.

654
00:31:40.570 --> 00:31:46.190
His observation haki is so good
that he's able to see slightly ahead into the future.

655
00:31:46.190 --> 00:31:48.260
His bounty is over a billion.

656
00:31:48.260 --> 00:31:50.500
He's a monster!

657
00:31:52.060 --> 00:31:54.820
I see. Alright then.

658
00:31:56.680 --> 00:31:58.440
It's about time.

659
00:32:21.910 --> 00:32:25.380
It's time for the tea party.

660
00:32:32.800 --> 00:32:37.220
Everyone! Thank you for coming all this way!

661
00:32:46.110 --> 00:32:53.820
Wherever you look, all you see are sweets!

662
00:33:01.790 --> 00:33:02.910
Eat!

663
00:33:04.710 --> 00:33:05.790
Drink!

664
00:33:07.540 --> 00:33:13.430
And enjoy the party to your heart's content!

665
00:33:14.340 --> 00:33:17.470
Enjoy everything...

666
00:33:18.180 --> 00:33:20.580
that'll take place here!
